<Program>       	        --> <recipe> 

<recipe>                    --> <title> [<descriptor>] <ingredients> <procedure> 

<descriptor>              	--> (<description>? | <amount>? | <time>? | <calories>?) {<descriptor>} 
 
<title>                     --> title: <text>

<amount>                    --> (<number> {<text>}) 

<relativeAmount>            --> rest | all | half | quarter 

<kitchenwares>              --> <name>[\?] {\n kitchenwares} 

<procedure>                 --> procedure: \n <step> {, <step>} <done> 

<step>                      --> <subprocedureHeader> \n [<procedureText>]\n [<yield> | <update>] 

<procedureText>             --> [<itemReference> | {<amount>} | <text>] {procedureText}

<itemReference> 			--> \[<ingredient> | <kitchenware> | <text>:<name>\]

<subprocedureHeader>     	--> (with(<procedureIngredients>) |using(<procedureKitchenwares>) | with(<ingredients>) using(<kitchenware>)): 

<yield>                     --> yield: \n <yieldIngredients> 

<update>                    --> update: \n <procedureIngredient> {\n yieldIngredient} 

<done>                      --> done\(<title>\) 

<description>               --> description: \n <text>

<prep time>                 --> prep time: <number>

<cook time>                 --> cook time: <number>

<total time>                --> total time: <number>

<time>                      --> <timeprefix>: <number> {time}

<timeprefix>                --> ((prep time)? | (cook time)? | (total time)?)

<calories>                  --> calories: <number>

<defineIngredients>         --> <name>[<ingredientOperator>] [<defineAmount>] {\n ingredients} 

<withIngredients>           --> <name> [<amount>] {, withIngredients} 

<yieldIngredients>          --> <name>[+ | <amount>|<relativeAmount>] {\n yieldIngredients} 

<ingredientOperator>        --> (+? | *? | \??) {operator} 

<amount>                    --> <number> <text>

<text>                      --> [a-zA-Z_ ]+

<name>                      --> [\w ]+

<number>                	--> [0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)? | [0-9]\/[0-9]
